    <description>
      Zeal is an offline documentation browser inspired by [Dash](https://kapeli.com/dash/), available for Linux and Windows.

      - Quickly search documentation using Alt+Space (or customised) hotkey to display Zeal from any place in your workspace.
      - Search in multiple sets of documentation at once.
      - Do not depend on your Internet connection.
      - Integrate Zeal with IDEA, Sublime Text, or your favourite IDE with a variety of [plugins](https://zealdocs.org/usage.html#plugins).
    </description>
    <summary>A simple offline documentation browser</summary>
    <releaseNotes>
      **New Features:**

      - Implemented update functionality for docsets installed via XML feeds. ([#289](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/issues/289))

      **Improvements:**

      - Added show/hide options to the tray icon's menu. ([#741](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/issues/741))
      - Tabs are movable.
      - Double click on the tab bar creates a new tab.
      - Web view now has a predefined list of zooming level.
      - Linux: Use dedicated tray icon if theme provides one. ([#770](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/issues/770))
      - Portable version now indicates so in title of the main window.

      **Fixed Issues:**

      - Fixed search result sorting with fuzzy search disabled. ([#679](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/issues/679))
      - Fixed invisible file operations preventing the Docsets dialog from closing. ([#608](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/issues/608))
      - Fixed crashing on some corrupted docset directories. ([#788](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/issues/788))
      - Fixed the app exiting on its own when a new version is available. ([#637](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/issues/637))
      - Windows: Fixed app not gaining focus when invoked from IDE plugins. ([#440](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/issues/440))

      **Known Issues:**

      - Open in new tab doesn't work. ([#851](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/issues/851))

      [Git history](https://github.com/zealdocs/zeal/compare/v0.4.0...v0.5.0)
    </releaseNotes>
